Distribution. RecordedfromthenorthwesternPacific off Japan and Taiwan as well as from the southeastern Pacific at the Sala y Gomez Ridge; depth range 514–1240 m ( Sazonov & Iwamoto 1992 ;
Shao et al. 2008a
, 2008b ; this study). In Japanese waters, known from the Pacific off southern Japan northward to the Miura Peninsula ( 139.62ºE ), Okinawa Trough, and off Minami-torishima Island, at depths of 631‾ 1187 m (Appendix 3-12B). It appears to be rare wherever found.
